    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has some mechanical issues that will likely require attention in the near term. The exterior shows visible wear including dents and scratches beyond normal use. The interior has noticeable wear with some damage to upholstery and trim. Suitable for a buyer willing to put some work into it.",
